# Easter Egg Treasure Hunt

Find all of the little eggs
Hidden ALL around this gallery, (You just need to count them and fill the form)

Bonus entry if you pay attention to how many types there are.

The elder tree awaits your answer (Roof- click the biggest tree for the link)

I'm extending the egg hunt until Thursday April 8th until I generate the winner.

Winner!!!- Clayboyn
